katie's parents were giving her drinks the other day! what is with y'all!?
I'm a drunk skunk. My cousin was making me take shots of patron in the kitchen.
Do skunks even act drunk? That's a silly expression
i think it has to do with the rhyming. they do kinda waddle, though. drunk people do that.
Do I waddle when I'm drunk? O_O I want a pet skunk.
i've heard skunks make great pets as long as you have them deglanded.
Oh god. I'm so weepy it's gross. I had to leave the reception.
why?!
Because this is the first of my cousins to get married, and it makes me sad to think of when we were still kids, her running around trying to brush my hair and
me screaming because I just wanted to play monopoly. She's like my sister. It's just so strange that we're grown up and things won't ever be the same.
aw. :( i can chase you with a hairbrush if you want.
